name: Zumba
description: All levels welcome. Move your body to the rhythm and burn some calories in this judgement-free ZUMBA class.

description: Beginner-friendly class that teaches you basic yoga positions and helps improve your strength and flexibility. Find your balance today!

description: All levels welcome. This cycle class incorporates various cycle rides as a high energy cardio workout for the entire body.

description: Prerequisite: Circuit training. Advanced levels only. This interval based class combines full body strength training with cardio bursts.

name: Pilates
description: All levels welcome. The basic method of mat-based core training which conditions multiple muscles in your body.

name: Tai Chi
description: Beginner/Intermediate levels welcome. Tai Chi is a chinese exercise that incorporates slow and repetitive low impact movements to achieve relaxation of both body and mind.
